00:00:12.279 --> 00:00:13.780
You're really ready
to move, huh?

00:00:13.780 --> 00:00:14.982
You bet I am.

00:00:14.982 --> 00:00:17.050
If I can beat the Laverre Gym
Leader

00:00:17.050 --> 00:00:18.952
I'm gonna win
my sixth Gym badge.

00:00:18.952 --> 00:00:21.421
Two more, then the Kalos League.

00:00:21.421 --> 00:00:23.857
Um‐hm. Then let's hurry.

00:00:23.857 --> 00:00:25.359
The Gym is that way.

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:26.493
Awesome.

00:00:26.493 --> 00:00:28.262
Serena's ready to move, too.

00:00:28.262 --> 00:00:30.664
You're that excited to see
a Gym battle?

00:00:30.664 --> 00:00:31.865
SERENA
'Of course.'

00:00:31.865 --> 00:00:33.066
'I'll be able to meet Valerie.'

00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:34.067
‐ Huh?
‐ Huh?

00:00:34.067 --> 00:00:36.370
‐ Who's Valerie?
‐ Look. Ta‐da.

00:00:36.370 --> 00:00:38.605
Here she is. Isn't she great?

00:00:38.605 --> 00:00:40.908
BONNIE
'Wow. Her clothes are so cute.'

00:00:40.908 --> 00:00:43.076
SERENA 'That outfit is
one of her creations.'

00:00:43.076 --> 00:00:45.546
'You see, Valerie is a famous
fashion designer.'

00:00:45.546 --> 00:00:47.014
'Isn't that amazing?'

00:00:47.014 --> 00:00:49.883
And she has her very own store
in the Laverre City Gym.

00:00:49.883 --> 00:00:52.519
Hold on. Are you telling me
what I think you are?

00:00:52.519 --> 00:00:55.022
SERENA 'Right. She's the Laverre
Gym Leader as well.'

