in Laverre City

00:01:40.801 --> 00:01:44.137
where Ash will battle
for his sixth Kalos Gym badge.

00:01:44.137 --> 00:01:46.607
Now that they know the Gym
Leader Valerie is also

00:01:46.607 --> 00:01:50.077
a fashion designer, what kind
of opponent will she be?

00:01:54.314 --> 00:01:56.316
Ah. Ta‐da.

00:01:56.316 --> 00:01:57.784
It's the Laverre Gym.

00:01:57.784 --> 00:02:00.654
‐ 'Whoa.'
‐ 'It's huge.'

00:02:00.654 --> 00:02:02.356
[gasping]

00:02:02.356 --> 00:02:05.158
Wow, I finally get to meet
Valerie.

00:02:05.158 --> 00:02:08.261
There's so much I wanna ask her
about the world of fashion.

00:02:08.261 --> 00:02:11.465
Do you mind if I visit her store
after your Gym battle?

00:02:11.465 --> 00:02:14.368
‐ Of course not.
‐ Hurray.

00:02:14.368 --> 00:02:16.169
Okay, Pikachu, let's go.

00:02:16.169 --> 00:02:17.270
[DETERMINED]

00:02:18.171 --> 00:02:19.506
Is anybody here?

00:02:19.506 --> 00:02:20.507
[clamoring]

00:02:20.507 --> 00:02:21.608
Huh?

00:02:22.809 --> 00:02:24.911
Do you think I should
take this outfit now?

00:02:24.911 --> 00:02:26.747
We'd better hurry,
or we'll be late.

00:02:26.747 --> 00:02:28.815
Go ahead and take that package.

00:02:28.815 --> 00:02:31.551
And all the accessories, too.

00:02:31.551 --> 00:02:32.953
What's going on?

00:02:32.953 --> 00:02:35.255
They all seem really busy
with something.

00:02:35.255 --> 00:02:38.325
Ah. They're all wearing
Valerie's designs.

00:02:38.325 --> 00:02:39.860
They're so adorable.

00:02:39.860 --> 00:02:42.029
SAWYER 'Please.
I have to have a Gym battle.'

00:02:42.029 --> 00:02:43.764
No matter what.

00:02:43.764 --> 00:02:45.666
I'm very sorry.

00:02:45.666 --> 00:02:47.501
You see, the Laverre Gym
is closed

00:02:47.501 --> 00:02:49.870
because we're having
an event here today.

00:02:49.870 --> 00:02:51.738
There's really nothing I can do.

00:02:51.738 --> 00:02:55.075
‐ Aw. Oh, man. Oh, man‐‐
‐ Wait, are you serious?

00:02:55.075 --> 00:02:57.244
There's really no way
to have a battle now?

00:02:57.244 --> 00:02:59.513
‐ Hmm?
‐ I'm terribly sorry.

00:02:59.513 --> 00:03:02.349
Come on, please,
I came all this way.

00:03:02.349 --> 00:03:04.084
Are you here for a battle, too?

00:03:04.084 --> 00:03:06.620
Yeah. I guess my timing's bad.

00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:08.355
‐ 'Hey.'
‐ Huh?

00:03:08.355 --> 00:03:11.858
That girl's a keeper.

00:03:11.858 --> 00:03:14.728
Please take care
of my big brother. Huh?

00:03:14.728 --> 00:03:17.764
Uh, please, I told you to stop
this a million times.

00:03:17.764 --> 00:03:20.267
But Clemont, she looks really,
really, really nice.

00:03:20.267 --> 00:03:21.501
CLEMONT
'I don't need your help.'

00:03:21.501 --> 00:03:23.804
'I can find my own girlfriend,
thank you.'

00:03:23.804 --> 00:03:25.505
‐ 'When?'
‐ Hey.

00:03:25.505 --> 00:03:27.974
SAWYER
'It's the Lumiose Gym Leader.'

00:03:27.974 --> 00:03:29.076
‐ Who, me?
‐ Huh?

00:03:30.444 --> 00:03:32.245
It's nice to meet everybody.

00:03:32.245 --> 00:03:33.714
My name is Sawyer.

00:03:33.714 --> 00:03:35.982
He came to challenge me
at the Lumiose Gym

00:03:35.982 --> 00:03:37.217
not too long ago.

00:03:37.217 --> 00:03:38.785
Yeah. And I lost.

00:03:38.785 --> 00:03:40.821
But I really learned
a whole lot.

00:03:40.821 --> 00:03:42.956
Nice to meet you.
My name's Ash.

00:03:42.956 --> 00:03:44.624
This is my partner, Pikachu.

00:03:44.624 --> 00:03:45.759
[EXCITED]

00:03:45.759 --> 00:03:46.893
I'm Serena.

00:03:46.893 --> 00:03:49.463
‐ This is my sister.
‐ I'm Bonnie.

00:03:49.463 --> 00:03:50.664
And this is Dedenne.

00:03:50.664 --> 00:03:51.665
[HAPPY]

00:03:51.665 --> 00:03:53.166
Glad to meet you.

00:03:53.166 --> 00:03:56.236
So if you're challenging Gyms,
how many badges do you have?

00:03:56.236 --> 00:03:57.637
So far, one.

00:03:57.637 --> 00:04:00.207
I really wanna get some more
battling under my belt.

00:04:00.207 --> 00:04:02.242
So you've done well since then.

00:04:02.242 --> 00:04:05.746
His Treecko's quite a unique
Pokémon and moves really well.

00:04:05.746 --> 00:04:08.348
Wow, Treecko's your partner,
huh?

00:04:08.348 --> 00:04:11.785
SAWYER 'Treecko was my very
first Pokémon.'

00:04:11.785 --> 00:04:14.321
But we've still got
a lot of work to do.

00:04:14.321 --> 00:04:16.022
I really wanna get stronger

00:04:16.022 --> 00:04:19.226
and then go back and challenge
the Lumiose City Gym again.

00:04:19.226 --> 00:04:22.095
‐ You'd be welcome anytime.
‐ Thanks.

00:04:22.095 --> 00:04:24.297
But what are you doing here now,
Clemont?

00:04:24.297 --> 00:04:27.000
I left the Gym
in my Clembot's able hands.

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:30.337
That's because I decided to
continue my journey with Ash.

00:04:30.337 --> 00:04:31.772
Hmm?

00:04:31.772 --> 00:04:33.406
That way,
I can get the chance to gain

00:04:33.406 --> 00:04:35.876
valuable experience
watching Ash battle.

00:04:35.876 --> 00:04:38.812
Uh‐huh.
Ash is really incredible.

00:04:38.812 --> 00:04:41.381
‐ He beat Clemont, too.
‐ Really? You did?

00:04:41.381 --> 00:04:43.350
And he's got five whole badges.

00:04:43.350 --> 00:04:45.452
Five badges? Amazing.

00:04:45.452 --> 00:04:48.655
I'm gonna do my very best
so I can catch up.

00:04:48.655 --> 00:04:52.058
Uh, I've still got a way to go.

00:04:52.058 --> 00:04:55.228
Guess my sixth gym badge will
have to wait until tomorrow.

00:04:55.228 --> 00:04:56.897
So what do we do now?

00:04:56.897 --> 00:04:58.331
[UNSURE]

00:04:58.331 --> 00:05:00.867
Well, we could go to Valerie's
store first.

00:05:00.867 --> 00:05:02.636
Good idea. Let's go.

00:05:02.636 --> 00:05:03.970
Alright.

00:05:03.970 --> 00:05:05.305
[chuckles]

00:05:10.243 --> 00:05:11.878
[Serena gasps]

00:05:11.878 --> 00:05:14.047
Wow, doesn't that outfit
look great?

00:05:14.047 --> 00:05:15.282
[EXCITED]

00:05:15.282 --> 00:05:18.118
It sure does.
You'd look great in it, too.

00:05:18.118 --> 00:05:19.686
You think?
Thanks so much.

00:05:19.686 --> 00:05:21.888
But that one's beautiful, too.

00:05:21.888 --> 00:05:22.956
[giggling]

00:05:22.956 --> 00:05:24.925
Those two certainly have
a lot of energy

00:05:24.925 --> 00:05:26.226
don't you think?

00:05:26.226 --> 00:05:27.694
They sure do.

00:05:27.694 --> 00:05:30.297
You know, I'm really glad
they're having such a good time.

00:05:30.297 --> 00:05:31.598
Yeah, me too.

00:05:31.598 --> 00:05:33.400
[HAPPY]

00:05:33.400 --> 00:05:34.467
Hmm?

00:05:36.469 --> 00:05:39.139
Sawyer, since we can't have
our Gym battles

00:05:39.139 --> 00:05:40.574
how about we practice some?

00:05:40.574 --> 00:05:42.342
Hey, that would be great.

00:05:42.342 --> 00:05:45.178
If it's alright with you,
could we have a Double Battle?

00:05:45.178 --> 00:05:47.681
‐ I've never had one before.
‐ Sure thing.

00:05:49.349 --> 00:05:51.618
BLOSSOM 'What do you think
of those two?'

00:05:51.618 --> 00:05:53.820
Aren't they totally perfect?

00:05:53.820 --> 00:05:55.822
I think they might work out.

00:05:55.822 --> 00:05:57.791
[chuckles]

00:05:57.791 --> 00:05:59.960
CLEMONT The Double Battle
between Ash

00:05:59.960 --> 00:06:01.862
and Sawyer will now
begin.

00:06:01.862 --> 00:06:04.598
Alright, I choose you two.

00:06:06.032 --> 00:06:08.168
Now, I'm counting on you
to win this.

00:06:08.168 --> 00:06:10.170
[DETERMINED]

00:06:10.170 --> 00:06:11.738
Sawyer, what about you?

00:06:11.738 --> 00:06:13.473
You'll be using Treecko,
won't you?

00:06:13.473 --> 00:06:14.841
Yes, of course.

00:06:14.841 --> 00:06:17.911
And the other Pokémon
is my secret weapon.

00:06:18.945 --> 00:06:21.781
[DETERMINED]

00:06:21.781 --> 00:06:23.383
Yup, there's Treecko.

00:06:25.685 --> 00:06:28.188
POKEDEX Treecko.
The Wood Gecko Pokémon.

00:06:28.188 --> 00:06:31.258
Numerous tiny spikes cover
the bottoms of Treecko's feet

00:06:31.258 --> 00:06:33.960
allowing it to walk on
ceilings and walls.

00:06:33.960 --> 00:06:36.296
And that other one
there is Bagon.

00:06:37.530 --> 00:06:39.966
POKEDEX
Bagon. The Rock Head Pokémon.

00:06:39.966 --> 00:06:42.335
Because Bagon dreams
of being able to fly

00:06:42.335 --> 00:06:45.739
it regularly practices
by leaping from cliffs.

00:06:45.739 --> 00:06:48.675
Alright then, battle begin.

00:06:51.144 --> 00:06:53.380
Bagon, Headbutt.

00:06:53.380 --> 00:06:56.116
Hawlucha, meet it head‐on
with Karate Chop.

