00:07:05.592 --> 00:07:06.593
[READY]

00:07:06.593 --> 00:07:08.028
You may have noticed my Bagon

00:07:08.028 --> 00:07:09.329
has a really hard head.

00:07:09.329 --> 00:07:11.064
Then check this out.

00:07:11.064 --> 00:07:12.933
Lots of Karate Chops.

00:07:12.933 --> 00:07:15.902
DETERMINED]

00:07:15.902 --> 00:07:18.672
[KARATE CHOP MOVE]

00:07:18.672 --> 00:07:20.140
[screams]

00:07:24.044 --> 00:07:25.946
[EXERTION]

00:07:25.946 --> 00:07:28.048
[PAINED]

00:07:28.048 --> 00:07:30.817
Whoa, Ash.
That was pretty impressive.

00:07:30.817 --> 00:07:32.919
We keep on trying
and we never give up.

00:07:32.919 --> 00:07:35.388
That's our battling style.

00:07:35.388 --> 00:07:36.690
[PROUD]

00:07:36.690 --> 00:07:39.526
I see.
Well, we don't give up either.

00:07:39.526 --> 00:07:42.963
Treecko.
Use Leech Seed, let's go.

00:07:42.963 --> 00:07:44.130
[LEECH SEED MOVE]

00:07:44.130 --> 00:07:45.198
Use Fire Fang.

00:07:45.198 --> 00:07:47.300
[DETERMINED]/[FIRE FANG MOVE]

00:07:48.468 --> 00:07:50.437
Frogadier.
Use Water Pulse.

00:07:50.437 --> 00:07:53.540
[DETERINED]/[WATER PULSE MOVE]

00:07:55.308 --> 00:07:56.543
[laughs]

00:07:56.543 --> 00:07:58.111
That was great, Frogadier.

00:07:58.111 --> 00:08:00.246
[PROUD]

00:08:00.246 --> 00:08:02.248
You work together perfectly.

00:08:02.248 --> 00:08:04.884
That's what I call
real teamwork.

00:08:04.884 --> 00:08:07.120
You've taught me a lot.
Thanks, Ash.

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:08.488
Hmm.

00:08:09.889 --> 00:08:11.224
I've got it.

00:08:11.224 --> 00:08:13.193
Wouldn't it be fun
if I wore one of those dresses

00:08:13.193 --> 00:08:15.128
when I appear
in the Pokémon Showcase?

00:08:15.128 --> 00:08:16.129
[EXCITED]

00:08:16.129 --> 00:08:18.798
I think that's such a neat idea.

00:08:18.798 --> 00:08:20.500
Ash, what do you think?

00:08:21.234 --> 00:08:22.602
Huh?

00:08:22.602 --> 00:08:23.770
Where's Ash?

00:08:23.770 --> 00:08:25.939
Huh? Look, Serena, over there.

00:08:25.939 --> 00:08:27.340
Huh?

00:08:27.340 --> 00:08:30.310
Right. Of course,
Ash is having a battle.

00:08:30.310 --> 00:08:32.312
What else?
That's what Ash does.

00:08:32.312 --> 00:08:34.647
Of course.
That's our Ash.

00:08:35.915 --> 00:08:37.784
So why don't we go over
and watch it?

00:08:37.784 --> 00:08:39.753
‐ Mm.
‐ 'Excuse us.'

00:08:39.753 --> 00:08:40.920
Can we talk for a minute?

00:08:40.920 --> 00:08:42.122
‐ Huh?
‐ Huh?

00:08:42.122 --> 00:08:43.390
Sure.

00:08:43.390 --> 00:08:45.291
There's a little something
we'd like to speak

00:08:45.291 --> 00:08:46.793
to the two of you about.

00:08:46.793 --> 00:08:48.094
We hope you don't mind.

00:08:48.094 --> 00:08:49.362
Huh?

00:08:50.330 --> 00:08:52.632
Treecko, Bullet Seed.

00:08:52.632 --> 00:08:53.967
[BULLET SEED MOVE]

00:08:53.967 --> 00:08:55.335
Dodge it.

00:08:56.870 --> 00:08:58.371
Smart choice.

00:08:58.371 --> 00:09:01.107
Grass type moves work well
against Water types.

00:09:01.107 --> 00:09:04.077
CLEMONT But that's only
if they make contact.

00:09:04.077 --> 00:09:06.246
Now, use Bullet Seed
one more time.

00:09:06.246 --> 00:09:07.380
[BULLET SEED MOVE]

00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:09.282
Get in there, Frogadier.

00:09:10.617 --> 00:09:12.585
It's gone. Huh?

00:09:13.053 --> 00:09:14.587
Up there.

00:09:15.021 --> 00:09:16.990
[SHOCKED]

00:09:16.990 --> 00:09:18.158
Treecko, Bullet Seed.

00:09:18.158 --> 00:09:19.426
Alright, use Cut.

00:09:19.426 --> 00:09:21.761
[CUT MOVE]

00:09:21.761 --> 00:09:22.762
Huh?

00:09:22.762 --> 00:09:23.997
[SURPRISED]

00:09:25.899 --> 00:09:26.966
[ATTACK]

00:09:26.966 --> 00:09:28.668
[SHOCKED]

00:09:28.668 --> 00:09:29.769
Treecko, no.

00:09:30.503 --> 00:09:32.005
[STUNNED]

00:09:32.005 --> 00:09:34.407
CLEMONT
'Treecko is unable to battle.'

00:09:34.407 --> 00:09:37.477
Thanks, Treecko.
Now, take a nice rest.

00:09:37.477 --> 00:09:39.746
‐ 'That's how Ash battles.'
‐ Huh?

00:09:39.746 --> 00:09:42.282
