because he always comes up

00:09:42.282 --> 00:09:43.750
with something surprising.

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:46.586
We do lots of special training
and thinking on our feet.

00:09:46.586 --> 00:09:48.721
So, then we can win,
no matter what comes up.

00:09:48.721 --> 00:09:49.789
[AGREEMENT]

00:09:49.789 --> 00:09:51.624
I see, so I guess that's how

00:09:51.624 --> 00:09:53.793
you're able to battle
the way you do.

00:09:53.793 --> 00:09:55.728
I'll make a note of this
experience.

00:09:55.728 --> 00:09:58.531
There must be an endless number
of ways to battle.

00:09:58.531 --> 00:10:00.300
Yup, so, Sawyer

00:10:00.300 --> 00:10:01.501
what do you wanna do now?

00:10:01.501 --> 00:10:03.470
I wanna keep on battling.

00:10:03.470 --> 00:10:04.838
Bagon, let's go.

00:10:04.838 --> 00:10:05.872
[DETERMINED]

00:10:05.872 --> 00:10:07.740
That's the spirit.

00:10:07.740 --> 00:10:08.908
[upbeat music playing]

00:10:08.908 --> 00:10:11.544
Huh? Oh, hey, what's that?

00:10:11.544 --> 00:10:13.580
[CURIOUS]

00:10:13.580 --> 00:10:15.748
‐ Huh?
‐ Huh?

00:10:15.748 --> 00:10:17.484
‐ Huh?
‐ What's going on?

00:10:17.484 --> 00:10:20.386
[indistinct chattering]

00:10:29.562 --> 00:10:31.331
VALERIE
'What should I do?'

00:10:31.331 --> 00:10:34.767
'I get an important show,
and then this happens.'

00:10:35.935 --> 00:10:38.037
[CONCERNED]

00:10:38.938 --> 00:10:41.941
[WORRIED]

00:10:41.941 --> 00:10:43.943
Thank you.

00:10:43.943 --> 00:10:46.045
[speaking in Pokémon]

00:10:46.946 --> 00:10:49.115
[RELIEVED]

00:10:49.115 --> 00:10:51.751
I know I have to do my best
for all of you

00:10:51.751 --> 00:10:54.354
and for my fans
waiting for me out there.

00:10:54.354 --> 00:10:55.555
[HAPPY]

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:02.929
Ms. Valerie, please excuse me

00:11:02.929 --> 00:11:04.330
but may we enter?

00:11:04.330 --> 00:11:05.765
VALERIE
'Yes.'

00:11:09.702 --> 00:11:12.805
Huh? Va...Valerie?

00:11:12.805 --> 00:11:14.674
BONNIE
'It's her.'

00:11:14.674 --> 00:11:18.144
BLOSSOM 'Ms. Valerie, I was
thinking of asking these two.'

00:11:18.144 --> 00:11:19.546
Hmm?

00:11:19.546 --> 00:11:22.549
[gasps]

00:11:22.549 --> 00:11:25.485
Hm. They should be perfect.
Good.

00:11:25.485 --> 00:11:28.221
Valerie, it's such an honor
to meet you.

00:11:28.221 --> 00:11:31.291
I'm a huge fan of every one
of your fashion designs.

00:11:31.291 --> 00:11:32.725
Really?

00:11:32.725 --> 00:11:34.027
Why, thank you.

00:11:34.027 --> 00:11:35.862
Aw. Of course.

00:11:35.862 --> 00:11:38.064
BONNIE
'That girl's a keeper.'

00:11:38.064 --> 00:11:40.133
Would you take care
of my brother?

00:11:40.133 --> 00:11:41.634
I'm a keeper?

00:11:41.634 --> 00:11:43.970
Ah, ah!
It's nothing. It's nothing.

00:11:43.970 --> 00:11:46.005
‐ Bonnie, stop it.
‐ huh?

00:11:46.005 --> 00:11:48.341
Well, you can see
how pretty Valerie is.

00:11:48.341 --> 00:11:50.476
[chuckles]
Thank you, dear.

00:11:51.978 --> 00:11:54.113
Aha. A Spritzee.

00:11:54.113 --> 00:11:56.316
And a Sylveon.

00:11:56.316 --> 00:11:57.650
[EXCITED]/[DELIGHTED]

00:11:57.650 --> 00:11:59.219
Yes, a Dedenne.

00:11:59.219 --> 00:12:01.854
Dedenne's a Fairy type,
just like you.

00:12:01.854 --> 00:12:03.957
[speaking in Pokémon]

00:12:05.158 --> 00:12:07.160
[SURPRISED]/[EXCITED]

00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:08.761
‐ Huh?
‐ What was that?

00:12:08.761 --> 00:12:09.762
Dedenne talk.

00:12:09.762 --> 00:12:11.864
[HAPPY]

00:12:13.099 --> 00:12:14.434
[chuckles]

00:12:14.434 --> 00:12:16.803
You see, the reason I wanted you
both to come here

00:12:16.803 --> 00:12:19.005
is I have a favor to ask of you.

00:12:19.005 --> 00:12:21.307
That is, if you wouldn't mind.

00:12:21.307 --> 00:12:24.110
Huh? Favor?

00:12:24.110 --> 00:12:26.579
ASH/SERENE/BONNIE/CLEMONT
"Who's that Pokémon?"

00:12:31.317 --> 00:12:33.653
ASH/SERENE/BONNIE/CLEMONT
"It's Bagon."

00:12:33.653 --> 00:12:35.021
[APPEARING]

00:12:39.025 --> 00:12:42.028
[cheering]

00:12:44.264 --> 00:12:46.933
‐ What's going on?
‐ I have no idea.

00:12:46.933 --> 00:12:48.801
[AMAZED]

00:12:48.801 --> 00:12:51.571
[cheering]

00:12:52.238 --> 00:12:55.275
‐ Huh?
‐ Huh?

00:12:59.078 --> 00:13:01.547
Ladies andgentlemen,
the time has finally come.

00:13:01.547 --> 00:13:03.983
We will be presenting designer
extraordinaire

00:13:03.983 --> 00:13:05.985
Valerie's newest collection.

00:13:05.985 --> 00:13:08.788
Uh, what did she just say
they're presenting?

00:13:08.788 --> 00:13:11.124
It's a fashion show,
displaying Ms. Valerie's

00:13:11.124 --> 00:13:12.759
newest design collection.

00:13:12.759 --> 00:13:13.926
Fashion show, huh?

00:13:13.926 --> 00:13:15.061
[CONFUSED]

00:13:15.061 --> 00:13:16.929
And it's just about to begin.

00:13:16.929 --> 00:13:19.932
[crowd cheering]

00:13:19.932 --> 00:13:21.768
KALI
'First, an elegant creation'

00:13:21.768 --> 00:13:24.337
'with an Azumarill pattern.'

00:13:24.337 --> 00:13:26.472
[gasps]

00:13:27.907 --> 00:13:30.610
[cheering]

00:13:30.610 --> 00:13:33.112
This stuff sure is popular.

00:13:33.112 --> 00:13:34.614
[AGREEMENT]

00:13:34.614 --> 00:13:36.916
[crowd cheering]

00:13:41.321 --> 00:13:44.524
Maybe, we should tell Serena
and Bonnie about this.

00:13:44.524 --> 00:13:47.260
‐ Uh, they're not here?
‐ And next up.

00:13:47.260 --> 00:13:49.829
Designs featuring the beautiful
patterns of Florges

00:13:49.829 --> 00:13:51.130
and Chingling.

00:13:53.299 --> 00:13:56.369
[laughing]

00:13:58.304 --> 00:13:59.639
[gasps]

00:13:59.639 --> 00:14:01.541
‐ Serena?
‐ B‐Bonnie?

00:14:01.541 --> 00:14:02.775
‐ Ash?
‐ Look, it's Ash.

00:14:02.775 --> 00:14:05.244
Look, see?
Aren't I cute?

00:14:05.244 --> 00:14:07.513
Bonnie, what in the world
are you doing?

00:14:07.513 --> 00:14:08.915
I'm modeling, of course.

00:14:08.915 --> 00:14:11.551
Yes, I know that,
but why are you modeling?

00:14:11.551 --> 00:14:14.787
I had no idea Serena and Bonnie
were models.

00:14:14.787 --> 00:14:17.323
You're travelling with
a Gym Leader and models?

00:14:17.323 --> 00:14:18.624
I'm completely jealous.

00:14:18.624 --> 00:14:20.727
No, not exactly.

00:14:20.727 --> 00:14:22.829
Hey, Serena,
what's this all about?

00:14:22.829 --> 00:14:25.698
The actual models weren't able
to make it today

00:14:25.698 --> 00:14:27.100
and then they saw us.

00:14:27.100 --> 00:14:30.303
So Valerie asked if we wouldn't
mind taking their places.

00:14:30.303 --> 00:14:33.406
[cheering]

00:14:41.080 --> 00:14:43.683
Ah. Valerie looks incredible.

00:14:43.683 --> 00:14:45.718
She does look incredible.

00:14:45.718 --> 00:14:47.653
That's Valerie,
the Gym Leader.

00:14:47.653 --> 00:14:48.955
[DETERMINED]

00:14:49.856 --> 00:14:50.857
Hi, there.

00:14:50.857 --> 00:14:52.291
Thank you all so very much

00:14:52.291 --> 00:14:54.961
for coming to my fashion show
today.

00:14:54.961 --> 00:14:57.063
Every one of my latest designs

00:14:57.063 --> 00:14:59.298
incorporates Pokémon motifs.

00:14:59.298 --> 00:15:01.734
That's because my philosophy
has always been

00:15:01.734 --> 00:15:05.138
'the true beauty
can be only found in nature.'

00:15:05.138 --> 00:15:08.641
Also, all of my creations
are carefully designed to look

00:15:08.641 --> 00:15:11.677
their absolute best,
when worn during battle.

00:15:11.677 --> 00:15:12.845
What did she just say?

00:15:12.845 --> 00:15:15.581
‐ 'It's finally starting.'
‐ Huh?

00:15:21.287 --> 00:15:22.388
Huh?

00:15:24.056 --> 00:15:26.492
That one, the boy in the front.

00:15:27.794 --> 00:15:31.264
‐ You with the orange tie.
‐ Uh, orange tie?

00:15:31.264 --> 00:15:33.533
‐ You want me?
‐ Yes.

00:15:33.533 --> 00:15:36.436
‐ Will you please come this way?
‐ Huh?

00:15:37.170 --> 00:15:38.171
Sawyer?

00:15:38.171 --> 00:15:39.439
[WORRIED]

00:15:43.342 --> 00:15:46.412
Uh, so what's this about?

00:15:47.747 --> 00:15:50.349
I would like to have a battle
with you right here.

00:15:50.349 --> 00:15:51.851
Here?

00:15:51.851 --> 00:15:54.454
Now, of course if it turns out
that you defeat me

00:15:54.454 --> 00:15:56.756
I'll gladly reward you
with a Gym badge.

00:15:56.756 --> 00:15:58.791
‐ Really?
‐ Huh?

00:15:58.791 --> 00:16:00.660
It's her custom.

00:16:00.660 --> 00:16:03.362
Valerie does this to demonstrate
how her creations

00:16:03.362 --> 00:16:05.832
always look their best
when worn in battle.

00:16:05.832 --> 00:16:07.433
This is my chance.

00:16:07.433 --> 00:16:08.568
I'll take everything
I've learned

00:16:08.568 --> 00:16:10.703
and win that badge for sure.

00:16:13.039 --> 00:16:16.476
And now, the battle between
Laverre Gym Leader, Valerie

00:16:16.476 --> 00:16:19.345
and Sawyer, the challenger
will now get under way.

00:16:19.345 --> 00:16:21.047
I'm ready to go.

00:16:21.047 --> 00:16:23.149
This is a one‐on‐one battle.

00:16:23.149 --> 00:16:25.318
It will be over,
when either side's Pokémon

00:16:25.318 --> 00:16:27.520
is unable to continue.

00:16:27.520 --> 00:16:29.155
‐ Hey, Ash.
‐ Serena.

00:16:29.155 --> 00:16:31.390
Sawyer is going to battle
with Valerie.

00:16:31.390 --> 00:16:33.860
Using the same rules
as a Gym battle.

00:16:33.860 --> 00:16:35.928
Sawyer can do it for sure.

00:16:35.928 --> 00:16:37.430
Now, Bagon, let's go.

00:16:37.430 --> 00:16:38.664
[DETERMINED]

00:16:38.664 --> 00:16:41.467
I wonder what Pokémon
Valerie's gonna use?

00:16:43.402 --> 00:16:44.637
Spritzee..

00:16:46.205 --> 00:16:47.573
...come out.

00:16:49.542 --> 00:16:50.743
[APPEARING]

00:16:50.743 --> 00:16:52.612
I think I know that.

00:16:55.248 --> 00:16:57.483
POKEDEX
Spritzee. The Perfume Pokémon.

00:16:57.483 --> 00:16:59.785
Spritzee gives off a fragrance
that delights anyone

00:16:59.785 --> 00:17:01.420
who smells it,
which changes depending on

00:17:01.420 --> 00:17:03.289
what Spritzee eats.

00:17:03.289 --> 00:17:05.658
‐ This could be very bad.
‐ Huh?

00:17:05.658 --> 00:17:06.926
What do you mean bad?

00:17:09.395 --> 00:17:11.264
Bagon, use Dragon Breath.

00:17:11.264 --> 00:17:13.900
[DRAGON BREATH MOVE]

00:17:14.967 --> 00:17:17.670
Yeah. I landed the first attack.

00:17:17.670 --> 00:17:18.938
Huh?

00:17:18.938 --> 00:17:20.640
[HAPPY]

00:17:20.640 --> 00:17:22.208
How can it be?

00:17:22.208 --> 00:17:24.243
SAWYER
'I'm sure it made contact.'

00:17:24.243 --> 00:17:25.545
[HAPPY]

00:17:26.445 --> 00:17:27.880
[chuckles]

00:17:27.880 --> 00:17:30.383
Ah, you see,
Spritzee is a Fairy type.

00:17:30.383 --> 00:17:34.387
And Dragon‐type moves have
no effect at all on Fairy types.

00:17:34.387 --> 00:17:35.621
That's right.

00:17:35.621 --> 00:17:37.790
So that means
Bagon is in big trouble.

00:17:37.790 --> 00:17:40.660
This is going to be
one tough battle.

00:17:40.660 --> 00:17:44.530
Let's see. Dragon‐type moves
don't work on a Fairy type.

00:17:44.530 --> 00:17:46.966
I'll be sure to make a note
of this experience.

00:17:46.966 --> 00:17:49.735
‐ 'Look at Ms. Valerie.'
‐ 'So beautiful.'

00:17:49.735 --> 00:17:52.905
It's not enough.
Not enough yet.

00:17:52.905 --> 00:17:55.408
Not enough for my beautiful
battle.

00:17:55.408 --> 00:17:57.843
Now, try this. Headbutt.

00:17:57.843 --> 00:17:59.612
[HEADBUTT MOVE]

00:17:59.612 --> 00:18:02.248
And this. A continuous Headbutt.

00:18:02.248 --> 00:18:05.084
[HEADBUT MOVE]

00:18:07.987 --> 00:18:10.089
Spritzee never wastes
any movement.

00:18:10.089 --> 00:18:11.190
But how?

00:18:11.190 --> 00:18:13.759
It dodged every single one
of them.

00:18:13.759 --> 00:18:16.696
Now, I think that it's our
turn..

00:18:19.131 --> 00:18:21.867
...to make this battle
beautiful.

00:18:22.668 --> 00:18:24.236
Spritzee. Let's go.

00:18:24.236 --> 00:18:26.105
[DETERMINED]

00:18:26.105 --> 00:18:27.440
Don't let it get away.

00:18:27.440 --> 00:18:29.508
‐ Headbutt.
‐ Alright.

00:18:29.508 --> 00:18:31.210
Dazzling Gleam.

00:18:31.210 --> 00:18:33.546
[DAZZLING GLEAM MOVE]

00:18:33.546 --> 00:18:36.649
[crowd cheering]

00:18:38.517 --> 00:18:39.619
[gasps]

00:18:40.486 --> 00:18:41.654
[whimpers]

00:18:41.654 --> 00:18:42.788
[PAINED]

00:18:42.788 --> 00:18:44.123
Bagon, no.

00:18:44.123 --> 00:18:46.158
KALI
'Bagon is unable to battle.'

00:18:46.158 --> 00:18:49.128
The match goes to Gym Leader
Valerie.

00:18:49.128 --> 00:18:52.231
[crowd cheering]

00:18:54.400 --> 00:18:57.003
Bagon, you battled really hard.

00:18:58.704 --> 00:19:00.406
[groans]

00:19:00.406 --> 00:19:01.507
Hmm?

00:19:04.543 --> 00:19:06.178
Thank you.

00:19:06.946 --> 00:19:08.247
Hmm.

00:19:08.247 --> 00:19:09.949
Thank you very much.

00:19:09.949 --> 00:19:13.052
[crowd cheering]

00:19:22.928 --> 00:19:24.830
[crowd cheering]

00:19:24.830 --> 00:19:26.532
[chuckles]

00:19:29.068 --> 00:19:31.537
So that's the Gym Leader
I have to face.

00:19:31.537 --> 00:19:33.205
I've got it.

00:19:39.078 --> 00:19:41.213
SAWYER
'I learned so much today.'

00:19:41.213 --> 00:19:43.716
I would challenge her again
for sure.

00:19:43.716 --> 00:19:46.886
‐ That's the spirit.
‐ Good luck, Sawyer.

00:19:46.886 --> 00:19:49.355
‐ Man, that was good.
‐ Huh?

00:19:49.355 --> 00:19:52.024
Alright.
Time for some special training.

00:19:52.024 --> 00:19:53.592
Ash?

00:19:53.592 --> 00:19:56.095
I wanna be ready for my Gym
battle with Valerie.

00:19:56.095 --> 00:19:59.331
And that's gonna be really soon.
Let's go.

00:19:59.331 --> 00:20:02.034
[RAVENOUS]/[DETERMINED]

00:20:02.034 --> 00:20:04.637
Hey, Ash? May I join in too?

00:20:04.637 --> 00:20:06.539
You bet. That'd be great.

00:20:06.539 --> 00:20:08.574
You could really help us out
a lot.

00:20:08.574 --> 00:20:10.643
Ah. Thanks.

00:20:11.544 --> 00:20:13.379
Hey, what's the rush?

00:20:13.379 --> 00:20:16.382
It wouldn't hurt to take
the time for a proper meal.

00:20:16.382 --> 00:20:18.718
Ash has trouble relaxing
when he knows

00:20:18.718 --> 00:20:20.886
there's a strong opponent
waiting for him.

00:20:20.886 --> 00:20:21.987
Hmm.

00:20:22.588 --> 00:20:24.590
[chomping]

00:20:24.590 --> 00:20:26.292
Huh?

00:20:26.292 --> 00:20:28.461
Well, if that's the case,
I'll cheer them on.

00:20:28.461 --> 00:20:30.196
Okay, I'm coming.

00:20:31.130 --> 00:20:33.332
‐ Wait up.
‐ What, you, too?

00:20:33.332 --> 00:20:35.367
Guess I'll go, too.

00:20:35.367 --> 00:20:37.737
[chomping]

00:20:37.737 --> 00:20:39.505
Hey, wait for me.

00:20:39.505 --> 00:20:42.041
NARRATOR Now that Ash has
witnessed the incredible power

00:20:42.041 --> 00:20:45.311
of Valerie the Laverre City Gym
Leader, will he be able

00:20:45.311 --> 00:20:48.247
to defeat her and earn his
sixth Kalos Gym badge?

00:20:48.247 --> 00:20:49.815
The answer to come

00:20:49.815 --> 00:20:52.418
as the journey continues.

